  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe got OOM issue again in non-finality time in Medalla, did not do a memory inspection but I think in-memory block pool is not sustainable and we need to improve that first.\r\nIn my test, I got ~1000 gossip/pending blocks and it need to be ~8000 to catchup with head block/slot.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nI think \"BlockPool\" should maintain maps of block roots/slots, the real block data is stored in a new \"pendingBlock\" db (this is similar to forkchoice which is an index store vs \"block\" db which is real repo).\r\n",
